<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>결제 성공 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f3ef;
      color: #111;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    h1 { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #edf7f0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .actions {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .dark {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: #111;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>결제가 완료되었습니다</h1>
      <p>결제 승인 성공 후 주문이 확정되고 재고가 차감되었습니다.</p>

      <div class="info">
        주문 DB 번호: <strong><%= order._id %></strong><br />
        주문번호(orderId): <strong><%= order.merchantUid %></strong><br />
        paymentKey: <strong><%= order.paymentKey || '-' %></strong><br />
        결제금액: <strong><%= Number(order.totalPrice).toLocaleString() %>원</strong>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="dark" href="/order/complete">주문완료 페이지 보기</a>
        <a class="light" href="/my-orders">내 주문내역 보기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>